msgid ""
"To activate any of the *Help Center* features on a *Helpdesk* team, go to "
":menuselection:`Helpdesk app --> Configuration --> Helpdesk Teams` and "
"select a team, or create a :doc:`new one <../../helpdesk>`. Verify the "
