"the project, and :ref:`costs <project/project-profitability/costs>` accrued "
"by your company. The same record can be displayed in both sections, e.g., "
"the same timesheet is listed under :guilabel:`Revenues` with the amount the "
"customer paid for the work and under :guilabel:`Costs` with the amount of "
"wages paid to the employees."
